  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Male or female eighteen (18) years of age or older

          -  Currently scheduled for a repeat endocardial ablation of AF where the index atrial
             fibrillation ablation procedure was completed ≤ twenty-four (24) months prior to
             enrollment and the subject has demonstrated at least one episode of post-ablation
             non-self-terminating AF

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  No more than two (2) previous left-atrial ablations

          -  Structural heart disease or implanted cardiac devices

          -  History of blood clotting or bleeding disease

          -  Pregnant or lactating (current or anticipated during study follow up)

          -  Evidence of left atrial thrombus
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
